# API routes ↔ D-WEB plan matrix

## Rule

Any PR that **adds, removes, or renames** a FastAPI route in **`api/routes.py`** must **in the same PR**:

1. Update the **§ Phase 0 deliverable — HTTP routes** table in **`docs/plans/PLAN_DASHBOARD_REPORTS_ACCESS_CONTROL.md`** (and middleware subsection if order changes).
1. Update **`EXPECTED_HTTP_ROUTES`** in **`tests/test_api_route_matrix_plan_sync.py`** so CI stays green.

## Optional micro-PR

If a route change is already merged, a **follow-up PR** may only refresh the plan table + test tuple — no product code — to restore sync.

